Notes: Nicole Greninger hit two free throws with 1:03 to play, breaking a 50-50 tie
to give Missouri Southern the lead for good.  The Lady Lions made 22-23 at
the line in the game, including 6-6 in the final 1:03...UMR hosts #5 Emporia
State Saturday at 1:30 p.m...UMR's Andrea Durante scores a season-high 19 pts.
